<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OGITECH Restaurant | Automated Food Management System</title>
    
    <!-- Premium Unified Browser Tab Favicon Icon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='%233498db'%3E%3Cpath d='M11 2v20H9v-2H7v-2H5v-2H3v-2H1v-2h22v2h-2v2h-2v2h-2v2h-2V2h-2zm2 5h4v2h-4zm0 4h4v2h-4zm-8 4h14v2H5zm0 4h14v2H5z'/%3E%3Cpolygon points='12,2 10,5 14,5' fill='%23d4af37'/%3E%3C/svg%3E">
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-master: #0a0a0c;
            --bg-surface: #141419;
            --crimson: #E63946;
            --text-main: #f3f4f6;
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;
            --border-glow: #2a2a35;
            --accent-gold: #d4af37;
        }
        body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg-master); color: var(--text-main); line-height: 1.6; }
        
        /* Premium Background Image Hero with Dark Overlay */
        .hero { 
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(10, 10, 12, 0.82), rgba(10, 10, 12, 0.95)), 
                        url('https://png.pngtree.com/thumb_back/fw800/background/20251008/pngtree-professional-chef-garnishing-dish-in-modern-restaurant-kitchen-image_19804215.webp') no-repeat center center/cover; 
            padding: 140px 20px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glow); 
        }
        .hero h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3rem; margin: 0 auto 20px auto; color: #fff; max-width: 950px; line-height: 1.3; text-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 40px auto; color: #d1d5db; font-weight: 300; }
        
        .btn-primary { background-color: var(--crimson); color: white; padding: 18px 45px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 8px; transition: 0.3s; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.4); }
        
        .section { padding: 80px 20px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
        .section h2 { color: var(--crimson); font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 15px; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
        .section-subtitle { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 50px; font-size: 1rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
        
        /* Interactive Culinary Grid Menu Section */
        .menu-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        .menu-card { background: var(--bg-surface); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-glow); overflow: hidden; text-align: left; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
        .menu-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--crimson); }
        .menu-img-wrap { width: 100%; height: 200px; background: #222; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
        .menu-img-wrap img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; opacity: 0.85; }
        .menu-card-body { padding: 20px; }
        .menu-card-body h3 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .menu-card-body p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .menu-meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px dashed var(--border-glow); padding-top: 15px; }
        .menu-price { color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .menu-tag { background: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.1); color: var(--crimson); font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 600; }

        .steps-container { display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 30px; }
        .step { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; background: var(--bg-surface); padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-glow); }
        .step h3 { margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #fff; font-size: 1.3rem; }
        .step-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        footer { background: #050505; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; padding: 50px 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glow); font-size: 0.95rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>OGITECH RESTAURANT AUTOMATED KITCHEN PORTAL<br><span style="color: var(--crimson); font-size: 2rem;">(Smart Order Management System)</span></h1>
        <p>An intelligent scheduling system engineered to optimize food orders, minimize prep times, and secure instant transaction fulfillment.</p>
        <a href="/order" class="btn-primary">Order your meal here</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Brand New Premium Showcase Culinary Menu Section -->
    <div class="section" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glow);">
        <h2>Our Premium Culinary Masterpieces</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Explore a glimpse of elite culinary combos currently engineered and served live through our automated kitchen queues.</p>
        
        <div class="menu-grid">
            <div class="menu-card">
                <div class="menu-img-wrap">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604329760661-e71dc83f8f26?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600" alt="Jollof Rice Combo">
                </div>
                <div class="menu-card-body">
                    <h3>Signature Jollof & Fried Rice</h3>
                    <p>Smoky West African jollof paired with premium fried rice, succulent chicken, and sweet fried plantains.</p>
                    <div class="menu-meta">
                        <span class="menu-price">₦3,000</span>
                        <span class="menu-tag">Chef's Choice</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="menu-card">
                <div class="menu-img-wrap">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546069901-ba9599a7e63c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600" alt="Amala Special">
                </div>
                <div class="menu-card-body">
                    <h3>Abula Special Sovereign</h3>
                    <p>Traditional piping hot Amala served with fluffy Gbegiri, smooth Ewedu sauce, and rich tender Ogunfe meat.</p>
                    <div class="menu-meta">
                        <span class="menu-price">₦3,000</span>
                        <span class="menu-tag">Traditional Elite</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-card">
                <div class="menu-img-wrap">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512152272829-e3139592d56f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600" alt="Crispy Platter">
                </div>
                <div class="menu-card-body">
                    <h3>Crispy Chicken & Chips Platter</h3>
                    <p>Golden-fried crunch chicken breast strips paired with salted skin-on gourmet potato chips and dipping sauce.</p>
                    <div class="menu-meta">
                        <span class="menu-price">₦2,500</span>
                        <span class="menu-tag">Quick Eats</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/order" class="btn-primary" style="background: transparent; border: 2px solid var(--crimson); color: var(--crimson);">View Entire Interactive Menu</a>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Core Architectural Modules</h2>
        <div class="steps-container">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon">📱</div>
                <h3>1. Order Ingestion</h3>
                <p>Customers submit automated food processing jobs tied to distinct volume criteria via the interactive terminal.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon">📊</div>
                <h3>2. Queue Scheduling</h3>
                <p>The processing engine automatically sorts incoming food payloads using comparative SJF and FIFO scheduling algorithms.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon">🛍️</div>
                <h3>3. Token Verification</h3>
                <p>Secure webhooks instantly process state transitions, routing verified tokens directly to the kitchen monitors for dispatch.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 OGITECH Restaurant System | Core Food Operations Management</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>